\begin{frame}{No proportional hazards (wrt \sc Hisclass)!}

\begin{itemize}
\item Fit each {\sc Hisclass} \emp{separately}, for each time period.
\item Use the \emp{cumulative hazard} at 65 (or 90) for comparison.
